creator: Herbert Trench
description: LibriVoxvolunteers bring you 12 readings of She Comes Not by Herbert Trench. This was the Weekly POetry Project for June 19, 2016. Read in English by Allen Kelly; Algy Pug; Bruce Kachuk; Doug Fajardo; David Lawrence; Newgatenovelist; Garth Burton; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson; Matthew Datcher; SaraHale and Tomas Peter. Frederic Herbert Trench was an Irish poet. A number of his poems were set set to music and he moved into theatrical work for a few years. - Summary by Wikipedia For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
